---
title: Hoisin Stir-Fry with Brown Rice, Sugar Snap Peas and Ginger
description: We get this stir-fry off  to a flavourful start with the aromatic trifecta of ginger, onion, and garlic. And although it’s got
all the traditional veggies you’d expect to find, there’s also some eggplant tossed in there for a new twist.
